  1101→
  1102→IMPORTANT RULES:
  1103→- Be SPECIFIC. Quote their actual words. Reference real answers, not generic advice.
  1104→- For filler_words: estimate counts based on patterns you see in their text (hedge words, qualifiers like "I think", "kind of", "sort of", "you know", etc.)
  1105→- For communication.score: evaluate clarity, conciseness, structure, confidence across ALL answers
